A tribute to the film director Sidney Lumet will be presented by the American Museum of the Moving Image on Nov. 11 at the Waldorf-Astoria Hotel. Mr. Lumet is noted for filming many of his more than 30 films in New York City.

The tribute will feature clips from Mr. Lumet's films.

Tickets to the tribute are $275 and $500; proceeds will benefit the museum. Information: 245-6570.